WEBVTT

1
00:03:27.250 --> 00:03:29.760 
到头来我觉得有点不舒服
and I wind up feeling a little sick.

2
00:03:30.000 --> 00:03:32.050 
继续做你现在所做的事
Just keep doing what you're doing.

3
00:03:32.770 --> 00:03:34.110 
我会想办法的
I'll figure it out.

4
00:03:35.830 --> 00:03:37.980 
把房子卖了怎么样  你一定想到过
How about the house? It has to have occurred to you.

5
00:03:37.980 --> 00:03:39.100 
是啊
Oh, yeah.

6
00:03:39.570 --> 00:03:41.900 
能解决很多问题
Oh, it would solve a lot of problems.

7
00:03:42.930 --> 00:03:44.160 
经济上的问题
Financially.

8
00:03:44.960 --> 00:03:46.630 
你是担心温蒂不想卖吗
Are you worried Wendy wouldn't want to sell?

9
00:03:47.160 --> 00:03:48.210 
不是
No.

10
00:03:49.610 --> 00:03:51.670 
我担心的是她根本就不在乎
I'm worried she wouldn't care.

11
00:03:53.470 --> 00:03:54.570 
你们是在这里看着你们的孩子长大的
You're raising your children here.

12
00:03:54.570 --> 00:03:57.100 
相信我  这房子对你对她一样重要
Trust me, it matters just as much to her as it does to you.

13
00:03:57.100 --> 00:03:58.290 
但那并不意味着她看不到
That doesn't mean she wouldn't see

14
00:03:58.300 --> 00:04:00.040 
现在正是卖房子的好时候
the wisdom of putting it on the market.

